N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 610.8 - Filing

State Regulations

Every application in this department
for a license as a legal consultant, together with all the papers submitted
thereon, shall upon its final disposition be filed in the office of the clerk
of this court. Notes
